                    <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
                    <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>From the vSphere Client select the ESXi Host and go to Configuration &gt;&gt; Authentication Services.  Click Properties and change the "Directory Service Type" to Active Directory, enter the domain to join, check "Use vSphere Authentication Proxy" and enter the proxy server address then click "Join Domain".

