                    <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>When adding ESXi hosts to Active Directory, if the group "ESX Admins" exists, all user/group accounts assigned to the group will have full administrative access to the host. Discretion should be used when managing membership to the "ESX Admins" group.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
