                    <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
                    <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>From the vSphere Web Client select the ESXi Host and right click.  Select the "Add Diagnostic Partition" option configure a core dump diagnostic partition.

