                    <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Check_Content</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
                    <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>From the vSphere Client select the ESXi Host and go to Configuration &gt;&gt; Advanced Settings.  Select the Net.BlockGuestBPDU value and verify it is set to 1.

