From the vSphere Web Client select the ESXi Host and go to Manage &gt;&gt; Authentication Services and edit the Smart Card Authentication configuration to add trusted certificate authority certificates and select "Enable Smart Card Authentication" and click OK.

For more information see the vSphere 6.0 documentation on VMware's website.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
